-- Yankees Hire Ex-Cubs General Manager Hendry as a Special-Assignment Scout
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-01-31T21:59:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-31/yankees-hire-ex-cubs-general-manager-hendry-as-a-special-assignment-scout.html
The  New York Yankees  hired former
Chicago Cubs General Manager Jim Hendry as a special-assignment
scout, the Major League Baseball team said.  Hendry, 56, was fired by the Cubs in August after 9 1/2
years on the job.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  